OL,3,CCourt's ruling on inquiry into GAA
OL,4,Cofficial's killing 'wrong'
OL,6,FOrdering Northern Ireland Secretary
OL,7,FHilary Benn to set up a public inquiry
OL,8,Finto the murder of GAA official Sean
OL,9,FBrown was legally and constitutionally
OL,10,Fwrong, the Court of Appeal has been
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FCounsel for the UK Government claimed
OL,14,Fthe judicial direction should not have
OL,15,Fbeen made amid ongoing attempts to
OL,16,Festablish that a new truth recovery
OL,17,Fbody is capable of carrying out human
OL,18,Frights-compliant investigations into
OL,19,FTroubles-era killings.
