OL,3,CCourt's ruling on inquiry into GAA
OL,4,Cofficial's killing 'wrong'
OL,6,FTony McGleenan KC said: "The error the
OL,7,Fjudge fell into was approaching the
OL,8,Fcase on the basis that the last word
OL,9,Fhad been spoken.
OL,11,F"The court's determination is not the
OL,12,Flast word on compliance, it's the
OL,13,Ffirst."
OL,15,FIn December, Mr Justice Humphreys
OL,16,Fcompelled the Secretary of State to
OL,17,Festablish a public inquiry after
OL,18,Ffinding the government remains in
OL,19,Fbreach of a human rights duty to probe
OL,20,Fthe full extent of state collusion in
OL,21,FMr Brown's murder.
