OL,4,Cofficial's killing 'wrong'
OL,6,FThe victim, a 61-year-old father of
OL,7,Fsix, was abducted by a Loyalist
OL,8,FVolunteer Force gang as he locked the
OL,9,Fgates at Bellaghy Wolfe Tones GAA Club
OL,10,Fin Co Londonderry.
OL,12,FThe father of six was bundled into the
OL,13,Fboot of his car, taken to Randalstown,
OL,14,FCo Antrim, and shot dead.
OL,16,FNo one has ever been convicted of his
OL,17,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
