OL,4,Cofficial's killing 'wrong'
OL,6,FIt emerged last year at an inquest
OL,7,Fthat state agents were among more than
OL,8,F25 people linked by intelligence to
OL,9,Fthe killing.
OL,11,FAt that stage the coroner halted
OL,12,Fproceedings due to the extent of
OL,13,Fconfidential material excluded or
OL,14,Fwithheld on national security grounds.
OL,16,FHe wrote to the previous Conservative
OL,17,Fgovernment requesting the
OL,18,Festablishment of a public inquiry.
OL,20,FIn September, Mr Benn confirmed that
OL,21,Fthose calls had been rejected.
