OL,6,FHe instead recommended that the
OL,7,Fbereaved family should engage with the
OL,8,FIndependent Commission for
OL,9,FReconciliation and Information
OL,10,FRecovery (ICRIR), a new body set up
OL,11,Funder the controversial Northern
OL,12,FIreland Troubles Legacy Act.
OL,14,FThe Court of Appeal has already ruled
OL,15,Fthat parts of the legislation breaches
OL,16,Fhuman rights law, with the government
OL,17,Fhaving too much power to prohibit the
OL,18,FCommission from sharing sensitive
OL,19,Finformation and uncertainty about
OL,20,Feffective participation for next of
OL,21,Fkin.
