OL,4,Cofficial's killing 'wrong'
OL,6,FEven though the Labour government has
OL,7,Fpledged to repeal the Act, it intends
OL,8,Fto retain the ICRIR and is currently
OL,9,Fseeking to appeal the findings made
OL,10,Fagainst it at the Supreme Court.
OL,12,FMr Brown's 87-year-old widow, Bridie,
OL,13,Fmounted a successful High Court
OL,14,Fjudicial review against the decision
OL,15,Fnot to set up a public inquiry into
OL,16,Fher husband's death.
OL,18,FMr Justice Humpreys identified a
OL,19,F"clear and unambiguous obligation" to
OL,20,Festablish such a statutory probe.
