OL,6,FAs the fast-tracked appeal got
OL,7,Funderway, members of the Brown family,
OL,8,Ftheir friends and supporters including
OL,9,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,10,Fher Sinn Fein colleague, North Belfast
OL,11,FMP John Finucane packed the public
OL,12,Fgallery.
OL,14,F"The court ought not to have
OL,15,Fprogressed this case on this point
OL,16,Fwhile there was live appellate
OL,17,Flitigation. That is the will of
OL,18,FParliament." Mr McGleenan insisted.
