OL,6,F"There is a constitutional error in
OL,7,Fnot recognising... we have an
OL,8,Fappellate process which we are
OL,9,Fentitled to exhaust and must be
OL,10,Fexhausted before you make any remedial
OL,11,Forder."
OL,13,FAt one stage it was put to him by the
OL,14,Fpanel of three appeal judges that the
OL,15,Flaw has to be applied as it currently
OL,16,Fstands.
OL,18,FLord Justice Treacy also highlighted
OL,19,FMrs Brown's advancing years, adding
OL,20,Fthat "the clock is ticking".
