OL,10,F"One can't help but have sympathy for
OL,11,Fthe Brown family, but there is a very
OL,12,Fimportant point of principle that it
OL,13,Fwas an error for the judge to address
OL,14,Fthe case in the way he did," Mr
OL,15,FMcGleenan submitted.
